OL,3,CFootball fans clash with police after
OL,4,CMorocco knocked out of World Cup
OL,6,FA police officer has been hurt and
OL,7,Fseveral people were arrested after
OL,8,Fdisorder in London on Thursday night
OL,9,Ffollowing a World Cup match.
OL,11,FPolice and fans clashed on Edgware
OL,12,FRoad in London after France beat
OL,13,FMorocco 2-0 in a quarter-final match
OL,14,Fin Boston in the United States.
OL,16,FFootage on social media appears to
OL,17,Fshow flares being set off and missiles
OL,18,Fbeing thrown at officers in the middle
OL,19,Fof a London street.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
